  "text": "HomeCareersAutumn PR is seeking various levels of Beauty PR experts to join our ever growing team. Autumn PR is seeking various levels of Beauty PR experts to join our ever growing team. Working with some of the best in beauty, this is an opportunity to join a non-traditional agency that acts as a true partner to our brands impacting brand awareness and growth. Working with emerging beauty brands in addition to taking existing brands to the next level, we pride ourselves on being leaders in what is next in the space, and approach all that we do with a creative modern lens. Founded in 2009, the team is made up of strong talent with various PR backgrounds that enables us to provide a diverse approach to strategy, outreach, and execution.Resumes can be sent to info@autumnpr.com.Position: PR Assistant, Full Time NYQualifications:● Previous PR agency internship experience required● Knowledgeable in the beauty industry● Organized, hardworking and able to work in a fast-paced environmentRole \u0026 Responsibilities:● Assisting teams with a multitude of tasks including:   - Press clipping   - Awards submissions   - Mailers   - Daily product send outs and tracking   - Reports● Keeping beauty closet organized and fully stockedPosition: Senior Account Executive, Full Time NY or LAQualifications;● 3-5 years Beauty PR experience, agency experience preferred● Solid press relationships● Proven experience in securing press coverage, event planning, and strategy building● Has pulse on industry trends, influencer space, and industry talent● Ability to manage multiple clients in a fast-paced industry and environment● Creative ideas, leadership, and strong organizational skills a mustRole \u0026 Responsibilities:● Contribute to PR strategies across multiple accounts● Own editorial relationships and press coverage for multiple accounts● Assisting in client management● Overseeing event planning ideation and execution@autumnprScroll to ContinueRecommended ArticlesSubscribe to Our NewsletterAUTUMN PR IS HIRING A PR ASSISTANT IN LA/NYAutumn PR is a modern communications firm with a focus on beauty, wellness, and jewelry. Understanding that no two brands are the same, Autumn PR provides each partner with a tailored strategy inspired by bold, unconventional thinking.",
