jEyNjUyMDE4Mzc0ODEzMzEy/autumn-pr.webp 640w\"/\u003e\u003csource sizes=\"(min-width: 1240px) 640px, (min-width: 675px) 620px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_380/MjEyNjUyMDE4Mzc0ODEzMzEy/autumn-pr.png 380w, https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_620/MjEyNjUyMDE4Mzc0ODEzMzEy/autumn-pr.png 620w, https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_640/MjEyNjUyMDE4Mzc0ODEzMzEy/autumn-pr.png 640w\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"autumn pr\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/t_share/MjEyNjUyMDE4Mzc0ODEzMzEy/autumn-pr.png\" data-src=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjEyNjUyMDE4Mzc0ODEzMzEy/autumn-pr.png\" height=\"662\" width=\"640\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" itemprop=\"contentUrl url\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/phoenix-picture\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.autumnpr.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eAutumn PR\u003c/a\u003e is seeking various levels of Beauty PR experts to join our ever growing team. Working with some of the best in beauty, this is an opportunity to join a non-traditional agency that acts as a true partner to our brands impacting brand awareness and growth. Working with emerging beauty brands in addition to taking existing brands to the next level, we pride ourselves on being leaders in what is next in the space, and approach all that we do with a creative modern lens. Founded in 2009, the team is made up of strong talent with various PR backgrounds that enables us to provide a diverse approach to strategy, outreach, and execution.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cu\u003e\u003c/u\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eResumes can be sent to \u003ca href=\"mailto:info@autumnpr.com\"\u003einfo@autumnpr.com\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePosition: PR Assistant, Full Time NY\u003c/strong\u003eQualifications:\u003cbr/\u003e● Previous PR agency internship experience required\u003cbr/\u003e● Knowledgeable in the beauty industry\u003cbr/\u003e● Organized, hardworking and able to work in a fast-paced environment\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eRole \u0026amp; Responsibilities:\u003cbr/\u003e● Assisting teams with a multitude of tasks including:\u003cbr/\u003e   - Press clipping\u003cbr/\u003e   - Awards submissions\u003cbr/\u003e   - Mailers\u003cbr/\u003e   - Daily product send outs and tracking\u003cbr/\u003e   - Reports\u003cbr/\u003e● Keeping beauty closet organized and fully stocked\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePosition: Senior Account Executive, Full Time NY or LA\u003c/strong\u003eQualifications;\u003cbr/\u003e● 3-5 years Beauty PR experience, agency experience preferred\u003cbr/\u003e● Solid press relationships\u003cbr/\u003e● Proven experience in securing press coverage, event planning, and strategy building\u003cbr/\u003e● Has pulse on industry trends, influencer space, and industry talent\u003cbr/\u003e● Ability to manage multiple clients in a fast-paced industry and environment\u003cbr/\u003e● Creative ideas, leadership, and strong organizational skills a must\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eRole \u0026amp; Responsibilities:\u003cbr/\u003e● Contribute to PR strategies across multiple accounts\u003cbr/\u003e● Own editorial relationships and press coverage for multiple accounts\u003cbr/\u003e● Assisting in client management\u003cbr/\u003e● Overseeing event planning ideation and execution\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/autumnpr/?hl=en\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e@autumnpr\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003csection id=\"phx-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\